data.description: Come see genuine sellers’ pride in this meticulously kept Horizon Pointe home that offers a range of welcoming features such as 10ft ceilings, easy-clean laminate hardwood floors, an eat-in kitchen with modern appliances, a formal dining room, a large living room warmed by a gas fireplace, three bedrooms that includes a baffling master suite with a 5-piece bath.  The upstairs laundry room includes a washer and dryer as well.  The garage’s character is introduced by its brick veneer wall and hanging Craftsman shelves that are transferable. The proximity to amenities, shopping, I-5, and JBLM is a practical advantage, making daily commuting and access to essentials more convenient.
